---
title: Pan-Seared Shrimp and Zesty Garlic Drizzle with Potato Coins and Citrus Salad
description: Simple shrimp is brought to life with a zesty garlic drizzle! Paired with a citrus salad and crunchy sunflower seeds, this is a perfect, bright plate for any meal.
